Nodes.Comment: This Heart will be completed later, just turn-in the Plants and Whetstones and continue. You can [weapon-swap] take them.
Turn in Plants and Whetstones here.
Glide off of the Launch Pad.
Open all the cages first then AoE all the little Crabs at once.
You can [weapon-swap] clear the Debris. Ignore the Skelk.
Click the Cave In's once and move on, there is a delay.
Make sure to loot all Fallen Soldiers on the way.
Do the event here to complete the Heart if it's up, otherwise leave it incomplete for now and move on.
Continue with the route after this if you're still missing a Heart.

DetachedNodes.Comment: Give all your [Seraph Badges] to the Heart NPC this way if you did the event earlier and completed the related Heart.
Target the Rat above and spam 2 from right here, out of LoS, until the Heart is done.
